<h2>Welcome to NeighborTools, @Model.UserName!</h2>

<p>
    Thank you for joining our community of neighbors who share and borrow tools. 
    We're excited to have you on board!
</p>

<p>
    NeighborTools makes it easy to:
</p>

<ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li><strong>Save Money:</strong> Borrow tools instead of buying ones you'll rarely use</li>
    <li><strong>Earn Extra Income:</strong> Rent out your tools when you're not using them</li>
    <li><strong>Build Community:</strong> Connect with neighbors and strengthen local relationships</li>
    <li><strong>Reduce Waste:</strong> Share resources and reduce environmental impact</li>
</ul>

